| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3354 — Recovery Inhibition (cicada3301)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9c790ff3-e98a-51c2-9d7c-7b775493780e"
